snippet.textDisplay: You talk about respect for the queen, it would have been a good thing if the queen showed the people some respect, for a woman who took a vow to serve us every day of her life, why did she not show us some respect when Diana died. Up until the queen took Diana's HRH away, I was a true Royalist, in the days when the National Anthem was played at the end of the days transmission on the TV I would always stand until it went off, so this attitude I have now is down to the queens own behavior.
